metadata.name: Not alone.
metadata.description:
this is my submission for #GalverseArtMatsuri contest.

I tried to paint this hoping that when they are alone and lonely, they would look up into space and feel the energy of the other gals( may send it back) or think "mother " through their energy.

the character :
